&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;菜鸟教程：&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucnVub29iLmNvbS9qYXZhL2phdmEtbmV0d29ya2luZy5odG1s&#34;&gt;https://www.runoob.com/java/java-networking.html&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
