&lt;p&gt;Java 全栈知识体系：&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9wZGFpLnRlY2gvbWQvamF2YS9pby9qYXZhLWlvLWJpby5odG1s&#34;&gt;https://pdai.tech/md/java/io/java-io-bio.html&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
